{"tid":1004213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple冇人買！】iPhone 7以下不再支持！外媒爆料蘋果iOS 13最新消息","createTime":"2019-02-01T09:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:22:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":112,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"342008da7bc8b2096cc2088518d6e6ca58994ee1","tid":1004213,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"IT之家2月1日消息 按照以往的慣例，蘋果將會在今年6月份的WWDC2019開發者大會上發布新一代的iOS 13系統。關於iOS 13系統，今日，以色列網站The Verifier報告稱，全新系統將會停止支持大量的iPhone和iPad機型。<br />\n<br />\niPhone方面，The Verifier報告指出，iOS 13將不再支持iPhone 5s、iPhone SE、iPhone 6、iPhone 6 Plus、iPhone 6s和iPhone 6s Plus，意味著3代iPhone產品將直接停止支持。<br />\n<br />\niPad方面，iPad mini 2、iPad mini 3、iPad Air、iPad Air 2以及iPad mini 4等機型也將不再受到支持；iPod方面，最新一代的iPod touch也將面臨停更，這意味著如果蘋果不再推出新的產品，iPod touch系列產品的支持也就到頭了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/408/191.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F408%2F191.htm&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxspR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=f38b1917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/408/191.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2128d7eff0a70899e866881f0501a25b1cfa98ab","tid":1004213,"uid":19454,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"逼你換機or轉會 An"},{"pid":"e9449d9340b2a2ff21dca4c71b74a85b97fa9c17","tid":1004213,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"留名等睇一出成堆機變磚頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b19c3769b534afe7d8827ec43e62c4cd10cdb0","tid":1004213,"uid":109383,"like":6,"dislike":47,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"正常啦 粒u效能差咁多"},{"pid":"fca596580337736b089fc1b135366f824fda7f0f","tid":1004213,"uid":162272,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:28:44.000Z","msg":"岩岩先買左部二手SE玩"},{"pid":"997c4947ecbeb85f27ae7c49e3dd955e8d3b14d3","tid":1004213,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike